import { Fragment } from "react"; import React, { useEffect, useRef, useState } from 'react'; export default function Product() { const [headerHeight, setHeaderHeight] = useState(0); const headerRef = useRef(null); const containerRef = useRef(null); useEffect(() => { // Function to set header height const updateHeaderHeight = () => { if (headerRef.current) { setHeaderHeight(headerRef.current.offsetHeight); } }; // Initial setting of header height updateHeaderHeight(); // Update header height on window resize window.addEventListener('resize', updateHeaderHeight); // Cleanup event listener on unmount return () => { window.removeEventListener('resize', updateHeaderHeight); }; }, []); useEffect(() => { // Apply margin-top to the container if (containerRef.current) { containerRef.current.style.marginTop = `${headerHeight}px`; } }, [headerHeight]); return (
